flowchart TD
    A[GitHub PR webhook event] --> A1[Signature and event validation]
    A1 --> A2[Fetch installation token and PR diff]
    A2 --> A2B[Retry transient opened-PR diff 404s]
    A2B --> A2C[Rebuild synchronize diffs from exact base and head SHAs]
    A2C --> A3[Fast relevance gate]

    A3 -->|Not AI relevant| Z1[Exit: no audit comment]
    A3 -->|AI relevant| Q1[Create audit job]
    Q1 --> Q1A[Revive failed same-SHA job when applicable]
    Q1A --> Q2[Job queue / work scheduler]
    Q2 --> Q2A[Atomic job claim]
    Q2A --> Q3[Background audit worker]

    Q3 --> B[Diff ingestion]
    B --> C[File and hunk extraction]
    C --> D[Structured change extraction]

    D --> R[History and baseline retrieval]
    D --> S[Static design profile extraction]
    D --> X[Semantic context selector]
    D --> F[Deterministic signal engine]
    R --> X
    R --> F
    R --> S
    X --> X1[diff_only]
    X --> X2[section_context]
    X --> X3[full_artifact_compare]
    X1 --> Y[Semantic review package builder]
    X2 --> Y
    X3 --> Y
    Y --> G[LLM semantic reviewer]

    F --> F1[File type classification]
    F --> F2[Guardrail and policy rules]
    F --> F3[Model, tool, and data access rules]
    F --> F4[Evidence spans and baseline score]

    G --> G0[Timeout and retry policy]
    G0 --> G0A[Honor provider retry hints]
    G0 --> G0B[Apply bounded retry window]
    G0A -->|LLM success| G1[Intent and authority change detection]
    G0B -->|Retry budget exhausted or permanent failure| G5[Preliminary deterministic audit]
    G1 --> G2[Safety boundary weakening check]
    G2 --> G3[Sensitive capability expansion check]
    G3 --> G4[Structured semantic findings and confidence]

    F1 --> H[Signal fusion layer]
    F2 --> H
    F3 --> H
    F4 --> H
    G4 --> H
    G5 --> H
    R --> H
    S --> S1[Attribute profile builder]
