    S2 --> S3[Attribute deltas plus drift narrative]
    S3 --> H

    H --> I[Risk scoring and confidence calibration]
    I --> J[Reviewer-facing explanation synthesis]
    J --> J1[Decision-first reviewer summary plus collapsible detail panels]
    J1 --> K[Managed Markdown PR audit comment]
    K --> L[Upsert current-head comment episode and sync escalation label]
    L --> L1[Persist audit outcome or fail job honestly]

    Q1 --> P0[Operational queue store]
    D --> P1[Artifact lineage and version store]
    S2 --> P5[Static profile and delta store]
    I --> P2[Durable audit and finding store]
    J --> P2
    K --> P4[Audit comment record store]
    P0 --> Q2
    P0 --> R
    P1 --> R
    P2 --> R
    P4 --> R
    P2 --> P3[Cold snapshot and archive policy]
    P2 --> M[Trend and reporting layer]
    P5 --> M
    P4 --> M
    P3 --> M
    M --> N[Fixture set and policy tuning loop]

